These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, billiard
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, trance
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the fan of trance is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game         | poker | mah-jongg   | billiard   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk     | water | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | blues    | folk      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, musician, paramedic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, azalea
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the paramedic is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the paramedic##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the musician and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Job   | musician     | paramedic     | scientist      |
| Flower   | azalea  | amaryllis | rose |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
City: paris, hamburg, prague
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, february, december
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person traveling to prague and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating kale##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| City           | prague | paris  | hamburg   |
| Birthday   | may  | february    | december |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

