.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, emerald, fuchsia
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, british, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the british##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is between the paramedic and the canadian##2
4. the person who likes emerald is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Color    | blue       | fuchsia  | emerald   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Nationality     | british   | turkish | canadian        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

