.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann, bongani
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, indian
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the pakistani is between the fan of gospel and the bongani-smoker##2
3. the aristoff-smoker is the indonesian##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Cigar         | aristoff | dannemann | bongani |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| Nationality           | indonesian     | pakistani       | indian     |

