.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, bus
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, blend, havana
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person driving the bus is the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the fan of country is between the person driving the snowmobile and the owner of the horse##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Transport          | snowmobile | taxi | bus    |
| Cigar         | blend | havana      | aristoff |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

