.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, peach, radish
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice, iced-tea
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, egyptian, malaysian
1. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person eating radish and the spanish##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating peach##1
4. the spanish is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | radish      | peach   | artichoke |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | iced-tea | juice   |
| Nationality     | malaysian         | egyptian  | spanish       |

