House: craftsman, cottage, colonial
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, journalist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the craftsman house##1
4. the architect is between the cottage house and the person driving the taxi##2
5. the person driving the airplane is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Transport      | scooter       | airplane      | taxi      |
| House         | cottage    | colonial | craftsman      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

