.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, turtle
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking, video-games
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Pet          | hamster   | chinchilla      | turtle     |
| Hobby   | video-games  | rock-climbing      | hiking |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

