.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, whist
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, project-manager, social-worker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, sailing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, salsa, reggae
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the project-manager is between the engineer and the person playing backgammon##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person playing whist##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the social-worker##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Game       | backgammon       | whist       | canasta    |
| Job         | social-worker | project-manager | engineer |
| Sport       | lacrosse      | sailing         | handball |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | reggae            | salsa  |

