City: san-francisco, rome, liverpool
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, roller, airplane
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
4. the person driving the roller is between the person traveling to rome and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| City         | rome  | liverpool       | san-francisco |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Transport   | trike | roller    | airplane     |

