.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
House: victorian, futuristic, wooden
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, lily
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the wooden house##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the futuristic house and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| House           | victorian | wooden | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Flower   | iris  | begonia    | lily        |

