.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, june
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, water
1. the german is between the person drinking water and the egyptian##2
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of disco##1
5. the person drinking tea is the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| Birthday           | february        | june   | july  |
| Beverage     | water      | soy-milk   | tea |

