3. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the dunhill-smoker is between the oliveros-smoker and the person eating pepper##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar           | alhambra   | dunhill   | oliveros |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Food   | pepper     | lime      | pomegranate    |
| Pet           | goldfish | hedgehog | mouse    |

