.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, volleyball, rowing
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, trike, scooter
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| Sport   | volleyball        | water-polo       | rowing      |
| Transport           | scooter           | taxi    | trike       |

