.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, spinach, strawberry
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, game, old-henry
3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the game-smoker is the person driving the car##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the car##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the person eating strawberry##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is between the person driving the tram and the person playing scrabble##2
6. the person playing chess is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | spinach      | raspberry | strawberry |
| Cigar         | game     | old-henry    | alhambra        |
| Game       | scrabble | chess   | monopoly   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 